The paper deals with immersive video streaming, which involves multimedia processing and computer vision techniques (cs.MM, cs.CV). The paper also discusses the optimization of network resource usage, which falls under the category of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper involves mathematical modeling and analysis, which is related to information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the paper discusses the perceptual impact of quality variations, which is related to graphics (cs.GR).
